{"tid":359121,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"其實點解書面語要跟普通話嘅用字","createTime":"2017-08-14T08:46:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-23T18:51:10.000Z","uid":56308,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4ac8ec86dcb2107528231a97f37d49bccbcd6a37","tid":359121,"uid":56308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T08:46:15.000Z","msg":"廣東話：行路   普通話：走路<br />\n廣東話：飲水   普通話：喝水<br />\n廣東話：話/講  普通話：說<br />\n廣東話：食飯   普通話：吃飯<br />\n<br />\n以上只係部分例子。<br />\n<br />\n學校會要求我地作文跟返右邊嘅用字，唔好用行路、食飯等口語字。但明明佢地都係中文，都係字面意思上合理嘅用字。"},{"pid":"fa9cb40ca055d80a9654ee168d3b41575e4f22e5","tid":359121,"uid":8543,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T08:55:34.000Z","msg":"「書面語」是基於「現代標準漢語」為基礎發展而成"},{"pid":"de285c06e9fe904706b1d4950a457ba9012f0be4","tid":359121,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T08:58:16.000Z","msg":"普通話都有好多口語<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔一定變書面"},{"pid":"2df9170614cb2f9c1998145806c35b829361958e","tid":359121,"uid":8543,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T08:59:39.000Z","msg":"標準化嘅統一書面語和文字有助迷惑民眾誤會係同一語言<br />\nFor維穩"},{"pid":"e4767ddb79362788772dafe12a7fcef2455679f7","tid":359121,"uid":92353,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T09:21:45.000Z","msg":"因為有軍隊同冇軍隊支持嘅分別"},{"pid":"8d40f289f2cb85d89b8ca9058734f12888508427","tid":359121,"uid":17008,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T09:49:57.000Z","msg":"上面除左 講話/說 外都係絕佳例子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c427af15288069c56bc68e04ca2e3e05b72f2c43","tid":359121,"uid":56308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T11:55:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>上面除左 講話/說 外都係絕佳例子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n敢問用講/話黎取代說有咩問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8